# Goals

## UiSystem-G1 Responsive and Accessible Frontend
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Chat-G1, Specs-G2, Relay-G3

The frontend must work for the boss on a laptop, the engineer on a tablet, and the contributor with a keyboard or screen reader.
---

## UiSystem-G2 Layout adapts to desktop, tablet, and mobile breakpoints
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] Desktop (≥1280px): full 3-zone layout with sidebar + main + context panel
- [x] Tablet (1024–1279px): Zone C collapses to toggle drawer
- [x] Mobile (<1024px): single column with tab nav and bottom sheets
- [x] No horizontal scroll on any breakpoint
---

## UiSystem-G3 Keyboard shortcuts navigate between views without mouse
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] Ctrl+1 switches to Chat view
- [x] Ctrl+2 switches to Specs view
- [x] Ctrl+3 switches to Relay view
- [x] Ctrl+K opens jump-to-ID dialog
- [x] Shortcuts work from any focused element
---

## UiSystem-G4 Focus management guides users through gate approval flows
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] GateCard auto-focuses Approve button when it appears
- [x] Secretary message receives focus on arrival; Escape dismisses
- [x] Tab order is logical within diff views and expanded cards
- [x] Focus traps do not prevent reaching browser chrome
---

## UiSystem-G5 Screen reader annotations describe node graph and relations
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] Pipeline nodes have aria-label with profession + status + elapsed time
- [x] RelationsPanel announces "X parents, Y children" on expand
- [x] Live Log announces new entries with polite live region
- [x] All interactive elements have accessible names
---

## UiSystem-G6 Theme & Accent Color System
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-G1

- [x] Dark / light / system theme switching with `localStorage` persistence (VitePress-compatible key)
- [x] Five curated accent palettes (indigo, coral, ocean, sage, amber) applied via CSS custom properties
- [x] Theme class syncs to `<html>` element for Tailwind dark mode compatibility
- [x] Accent color picker accessible from app header/settings area
---

## UiSystem-G7 Explorer Module for VS Code–style File Tree and Content Preview
**Status:** implemented
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Project-G1

- [x] Recursive file tree sidebar with collapsible folders, file-type icons, and active path highlighting
- [x] Content preview pane supports text, images, PDFs, and download links for other file types
- [x] Client-side search filters tree nodes by filename
- [x] Close-project button in sidebar toolbar; project indicator in nav rail
- [x] Keyboard shortcut `Ctrl+0` opens Explorer view
